Willard Jackson is the founder of CVG Group, a private equity firm based in Houston. By specializing in acquisitions of U.S. based, middle market companies, CVG strategically invests in companies that benefit communities in the US, but when an unexpected day sent bad news to the door of one his businesses, Willard Jackson had to confront his worst day in business and find a way to overcome it.
